Game : Evolution 2
Origin : USA - NTSC
Released : June 29th, 2000

The sequel to our first DC release, This also hit shops today.

Game Info:
~~~~~~~~~~
Evolution 2 takes the hit Dreamcast RPG franchise to new heights -- a sweeping adventure where the power to destroy seeks the power to heal. In this new journey Mag must choose between his lifelong dream or Linear's salvation. And at the center of the conflict stands Yurka, a mysterious new force. To survive, they must learn the difference between what they see and what they believe.